        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *minor reinforcing wooden shield* (Hardness 6, HP 56, BT 28) is made with a sturdy but flexible wood found in Tian Xia. It\u2019s painted with bold, bright colors in the style of a fiendish tiger head. In combat, the eyes of the tiger seem to follow the opponent.",
